{"tid":673153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"土瓜灣90歲阿伯　涉後巷非禮3小學生被捕","createTime":"2018-05-21T14:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T15:39:13.000Z","uid":159163,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8cf705adbc1b46ff57c8c2ed9a5c2b98b475a122","tid":673153,"uid":159163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:53:47.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣下午發生連環非禮案！下午3時許，警方接報兩名6歲及一名8歲女童，於炮仗街懷疑遭人非禮，警方接報到場調查，一名90歲姓林老翁涉嫌非禮被捕，案件交由西九龍總區重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，該3名女童當時隨老師及另外6名同學，前往土瓜灣一籃球場打波，期間經過炮仗街後巷時，被一名從後出現的老翁摸肚、背部及膊頭。她們大驚呼叫，老師見狀立即喝止並報警求助。消息指，被捕老翁報稱無業，並無相關案底，事後向警方報稱，覺得該3名女童「好得意」才會犯案。"},{"pid":"e3e9a5bb57616dd4e79528c1594fb665c3f842dc","tid":673153,"uid":159163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:53:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180521/58221402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F58221402&d=QCkAzDZkjj3i0qnYFRiarSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=8bda7dee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F58221402&h=c48f7909\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180521/58221402</a>"},{"pid":"1b7f54d730de01591c8ea3d59c9bebc7571c9259","tid":673153,"uid":3302,"like":4,"dislike":18,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:55:01.000Z","msg":"處女蘿莉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想屌<br />\n又窄又緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459d7d502dcb5c1ee26ed54ccf4d31ced1b6f27d","tid":673153,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:55:02.000